---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Frontend Structure

App.jsx – Main app with routing

main.jsx – Entry point

index.css – Global styles

Components:

common/ – Common UI components (Button, Input, Card, Modal, etc.)

layout/ – Layout components (Header, Footer, Sidebar, etc.)

farmhouse/ – Farmhouse-specific components (FarmhouseCard, FarmhouseGallery, etc.)

Pages (by persona):

public/ – HomePage, FarmhouseListingPage, FarmhouseDetailPage, AboutPage, ContactPage

super-admin/ – DashboardPage, AdminManagementPage, FarmhouseApprovalsPage, UserManagementPage, AnalyticsPage

admin/ – DashboardPage, MyFarmhousesPage, AddFarmhousePage, EditFarmhousePage, BookingsPage, ProfilePage

Hooks:

auth/ – useLogin, useRegister, useAuth

farmhouse/ – useFarmhouseList, useFarmhouseDetail, useCreateFarmhouse, useUpdateFarmhouse

admin/ – useAdminList, useApprovalActions, useAnalytics

common/ – useWhatsAppRedirect, useToast

Services:

api.js – Axios instance

authService.js – Auth APIs

farmhouseService.js – Farmhouse CRUD

adminService.js – Admin APIs

whatsappService.js – WhatsApp logic

Store / Context:

authStore.js – User auth state

farmhouseStore.js – Farmhouse data state

adminStore.js – Admin state

uiStore.js – UI state (modals, loading, etc.)

Routes:

PublicRoutes.jsx, AdminRoutes.jsx, SuperAdminRoutes.jsx, index.jsx

Utils:

constants.js, validators.js, formatters.js, helpers.js

Assets:

images/, icons/

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 How to create full folder structure with one command
 BY one shell command by combining mkdir -p (for folders) and touch (for files).

